/**
 * FirestoreStateManager - Firestore-based session state storage
 *
 * Collection structure:
 * sessions/{sessionId}
 *   ├── (session document fields)
 *   ├── progressLogs/{logId}
 *   └── inputs/{inputId}
 *
 * Unified Epic structure:
 * epics/{epicId}                           - Single collection for all epics (MCP + UI)
 * epicTasks/{taskId}                       - All tasks (with epicId reference)
 * features/{featureId}                     - All features (with taskId + epicId reference)
